KZLEKS
Later I reached out to the ladieswho.tech community, invited a designer to join our team, and updated the resume using the team’s methods. We plan to redesign the interface and publish retina on all marketplaces.

KZLEKS
Now I decided to share some tips that I myself would have found useful a few months ago. First of all, I recommend talking to a mentor to everyone. The ability to ask open questions was very useful to me. At the beginning, everything was unexpected for me, when I studied these applications, everything was very complicated and it was not clear to me what was what, what function was needed for what, who the user was, who would use it, what is it for? I asked a bunch of clarifying questions and in the end everything became clear. In addition, I recorded all the brainstorming, questions and answers in notes in the cloud storage and referred to them again many times.

KZLEKS
After six months of working as a product manager, I am inspired, resourceful and ready for new projects.

